						<li>
							<a href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AIslands of the Feral Pigs%0D%0AIn Hawai‘i, people, pigs, and ecosystems only have so much room to coexist, and the pigs exist a little too much.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/features/islands-of-the-feral-pigs/" title="Share by Email" target="_blank">
